               <p>I was at the bank the 21st of August, between twelve and one o'clock, and one of the witnesses held up this snuff-box, and asked who owned it, I said, it was mine, and he gave it me.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17830910-86-person975">
                  RICHARD
                   FAIRCLOTH
